    "name": "消防模拟：火苗燃动",
    "steam_appid": 1669480,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669480/extras/554fb1ccb1e6cacdba2e511c4dba695b.poster.avif?t=1771924903\" width=1170 height=502 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669480/extras/554fb1ccb1e6cacdba2e511c4dba695b.webm?t=1771924903\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">团结一心，共同抗火。在《Firefighting Simulator: Ignite》中面对无法预测的危险，与队员一起扑灭可怕的火灾并挽救生命。在美国中西部的一座大城市扮演美国消防员，每一次出任务都将你的技能发挥到极限。在直观的合作多人游戏模式中，与3名好友一起、或借助游戏系统操控的队员的力量，以令人惊叹的视觉质量体验十万火急的消防任务。对抗狂暴且变化无常的火焰、高热和烟雾，这些都是通过虚幻引擎5支持的先进物理和图形系统实时模拟，让你以前所未有的方式身历其境感受消防任务。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669480/extras/95b26a180d3aa27d87cb0854743e35bb.poster.avif?t=1771924903\" width=1170 height=502 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669480/extras/95b26a180d3aa27d87cb0854743e35bb.webm?t=1771924903\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">你将在职业生涯中应对各种挑战性十足的情况，例如市民受困、电气火灾、易燃液体、油火、回火、闪燃和爆炸。带上正宗的消防装备，包括消防水带、锯子、哈利根铁铤、斧头或灭火器，并使用忠实还原的消防车和云梯车。运用正确的战术与方法，精准扑灭熊熊烈火。每个任务都会需要用到现实生活中的消防策略，例如排出空气以减缓火势蔓延、冷却过热的物体、锯穿障碍物、减少气流流动、选择合适的灭火剂等等。也要对迫在眉睫的危险迹象保持警惕，例如浓烟流入紧闭的门，就有可能造成重大灾情。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669480/extras/f796b8a0a66f0da1944acc8a6676cfa8.poster.avif?t=1771924903\" width=1170 height=502 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669480/extras/f796b8a0a66f0da1944acc8a6676cfa8.webm?t=1771924903\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">不过别担心，你可以在消防站中心学习如何灭火和正确使用工具，消防站中心是在紧急行动之余待命的总部，让你在任务间隙可以休息一下，仔细观察包括逼真Rosenbauer消防车在内的大型车队，接着选择下一个任务。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">因此当紧急呼叫响起，请依照最短的路线到达急救现场，一起灭火并挽救生命。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669480/extras/c9a7c3c5abe33a7556a2c7c24b15472c.poster.avif?t=1771924903\" width=1170 height=503 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669480/extras/c9a7c3c5abe33a7556a2c7c24b15472c.webm?t=1771924903\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">     </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >日常英雄：扮演美国消防员</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >点燃热情：在单人和多人模式下扑灭可怕的火灾</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >团队合作：4人合作模式</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >团结一心，共同抗火：在单人模式中，和游戏系统操控的队员组成小队</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >真实重现：使用美国领先消防品牌的装备，如HAIX®、Fire-Dex、STIHL和</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >快速反应：驾驶忠实复制的授权Rosenbauer America消防车，如TP3® Pumper、Viper®、68' Roadrunner等</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >职业生涯：有8个角色和不同造型套装可供选择</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >消防站：可在此中心学习技能和选择下一个紧急任务</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >模拟：拜虚幻引擎5的物理引擎所赐，可模拟出逼真的火焰、高热、水和烟雾</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >PC模组制作：创建模组任务并通过Mod io分享和游玩</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >主机模组制作：可从Mod io中心下载和游玩新的模组任务</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669480/extras/ce91670c81fba4b778aa6c19e197890b.poster.avif?t=1771924903\" width=1170 height=502 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669480/extras/ce91670c81fba4b778aa6c19e197890b.webm?t=1771924903\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
